WEBVTT

00:00:00.635 --> 00:00:02.683
Track 01.07

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:05.874
Ryan: Good morning.

00:00:05.985 --> 00:00:07.501
Is this the teachers’ room?

00:00:07.533 --> 00:00:11.162
Alice: Yes, it is. Are you a new student?

00:00:11.467 --> 00:00:14.190
Ryan: No, I’m not. I’m a new teacher.

00:00:14.274 --> 00:00:17.137
Alice: Oh, are you Ryan?

00:00:17.244 --> 00:00:19.236
Ryan: Yes, Ryan Robson.

00:00:19.430 --> 00:00:22.208
Alice: It’s nice to meet you, Ryan.

00:00:22.433 --> 00:00:25.576
I’m Alice Long, the school manager.

00:00:25.697 --> 00:00:27.062
Ryan: Nice to meet you, too.

00:00:27.285 --> 00:00:29.300
Alice: Where are you from, Ryan?

00:00:29.459 --> 00:00:32.354
Ryan: I’m from Leeds, in England, in the UK.

00:00:32.608 --> 00:00:34.085
Alice: Oh, right.

00:00:34.220 --> 00:00:34.950
Ryan: And you?

00:00:35.287 --> 00:00:38.554
Alice: I’m from Boston, in the USA.

00:00:38.606 --> 00:00:41.471
Ryan: Really? Boston’s a nice city.

00:00:41.538 --> 00:00:45.825
Alice: Well, your class is 1A.

00:00:45.945 --> 00:00:46.651
Ryan: OK.

00:00:46.930 --> 00:00:49.556
Alice: This is the class list.

00:00:49.604 --> 00:00:51.580
It’s a small class.

00:00:51.757 --> 00:00:53.987
There are eight students.

00:00:54.067 --> 00:00:55.503
Ryan: What countries are they from?

00:00:55.575 --> 00:00:58.939
Alice: Let’s see. Err…

00:00:59.333 --> 00:01:02.539
Ana and Sofia are from Italy.

00:01:02.727 --> 00:01:06.623
Lee and Ping are from China.

00:01:06.761 --> 00:01:09.658
Daniela is from Brazil

00:01:09.794 --> 00:01:12.461
and Manuel is Spanish.

00:01:12.531 --> 00:01:14.332
Ryan: And Alim and Fehim.

00:01:14.638 --> 00:01:16.432
Those are Turkish names.

00:01:16.488 --> 00:01:17.511
Are they from Turkey?

00:01:17.810 --> 00:01:19.596
Alice: Yes, that’s right.

00:01:20.378 --> 00:01:23.092
OK, this is your desk

00:01:23.140 --> 00:01:25.270
and here are your books ...